Number 1: Enjoy yourself to the fullest,

5
00:03:13,500 --> 00:03:15,800
その2 全力でコメントをし、
Number 2: Comment with all your might,

6
00:03:17,300 --> 00:03:19,400
その3 全力でスクショを撮り、
Number 3: Take screenshots with all your might,

7
